===Noun===
'''[[modal]] [[verb]]'''
#(''grammar'') Type of [[auxiliary verb]]. Modal verbs need to be used with other [[verb]]s in order for them to be functional. Their function is to express the [[mood]] a [[sentence]] or [[clause]] is in. Only one modal verb is to be used at any one time. There are eleven modal verbs:
#*am/is/are/was/were to
#*must
#*ought to
#*will
#*would
#*can
#*could
#*may
#*might
#*shall
#*should

